title: Afghanistan Money Supply M2
description: Money Supply M2 in Afghanistan decreased to 538086.30 AFN Million in the first quarter of 2021 from 575737.90 AFN Million in the fourth quarter of 2020. Money Supply M2 in Afghanistan averaged 309567.23 AFN Million from 2005 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 575737.90 AFN Million in the fourth quarter of 2020 and a record low of 52178 AFN Million in the first quarter of 2005. This page provides - Afghanistan Money Supply M2- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Da Afghanistan Bank
